It's the back to school sale! Shop snacks for school, or shop CBD to relief some stress! Take 30% off sitewide using code BackToSchool at checkout. 

Through 8/29, we are donating 10% of all sales to the Hawai'i Community Foundation to support relief efforts in Maui. 

You can also donate directly to the Hawai'i Community Foundation here: https://www.hawaiicommunityfoundation.org/maui-strong
